text: Did not know this nursery is open to public. We happened to drive past and decided to turn in. Turns out they are having a clearance sale with 50% off all plants! So we snagged these 3 variegated philodendrons üëçüèª female boss was friendly and they have a huge variety of plants!
Good place to find the plants I need for indoor and outdoor plant, and surprisingly their nursery are open to public everyday
Very nice farm alot of plants and decor, a very relaxing garden and plants are not expensive.. Price reasonable and plants are very nice... Boss also very friendly.

Lots of plants to browse and buy. Price wise is very cheap compare to other nursery. Love this place so much. Been there many time to add plants to my collection and good variety of pots. Just bring along johnson off to scare off mozzie.
A variety of flowers and potted plants.
